{"tid":1331111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[催淚彈討論] 對付催淚彈應該用全濕毛巾覆蓋加灌水","createTime":"2019-07-18T23:00:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T11:57:16.000Z","uid":122054,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"758dcac47574277ef8da468a6a8bcb580a68095f","tid":1331111,"uid":122054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T23:00:41.000Z","msg":"我就讀物理既<br />\n火三角 要 熱力、氧氣同燃料<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oS96wFV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoS96wFV.jpg&h=58bc475f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n燃燒中既催淚彈既構成有: 熱力、氧氣同火藥，<br />\n以燃燒方式加熱釋放腐蝕性酸性催淚氣體，<br />\n達致crowd control既效果<br />\n<br />\n濕毛巾+灌水方法 可以完整覆蓋/大部分覆蓋催淚彈頭 (大型手擲式都ok)<br />\n達到高速降溫同隔絕氧氣，<br />\n可以令催淚彈迅速收皮<br />\n<br />\n如果大家認為可行既不妨納入濕毛巾做物資<br />\n或試下實戰用<br />\n真心應該work.<br />\n<br />\n希望721用得著啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8bfb74d135532611f1afa79b6fae43fd15a2526","tid":1331111,"uid":162347,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T23:05:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1629f570aaed66f0609caab16c9b452e0f38095b","tid":1331111,"uid":274911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T23:24:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等我為大家回憶下決定721去定唔去<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1324531/page/5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1324531/page/5</a><br />\n<br />\n[721] 和理非之所以企出嚟 唔係想勇武以死相博 而係想大家一齊凱旋歸來<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dkBgNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dkBgNS</a><br />\n<br />\n[7.21] 同我推返哂721上熱門<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dkeybS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dkeybS</a><br />\n<br />\n【香城OL wiki】史上最全攻略！！持續更新！！！<br />\n<